\section{Install R}

To install R, go to \href{http://cran.rstudio.com/}{R Cran}.\\
\begin{itemize}
  \item You must have R ($\ge 3.0.2$), to check which version you have, in R type
  <<eval=FALSE, prompt=TRUE>>=
  sessionInfo()
  @
  
\end{itemize}

